        "subject": "LU-3496 ost: various optimizations and cleanup for OSS",
        "message": "LU-3496 ost: various optimizations and cleanup for OSS\n\nThis patch does the following:\n1) removes unnecessary multiplication in filter_do_bio\n2) implements log2 with bitops in lprocfs_oh_tally_log2\n3) converts devlock into rwlock for *rdonly*\n4) cleans up f_e_m_ext_inode_pages\n5) optimize lprocfs counters in filter_preprw_read\n6) remove meaningless assert for dr_pages filter_do_bio\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Perepechko <andrew_perepechko@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexander Boyko <Alexander_Boyko@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: alexander_zarochentsev@xyratex.com\nReviewed-by: Vitaly Fertman <Vitaly_Fertman@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-999\nChange-Id: I33147ec61ae23aca2e6a2a8b334a930bf0eace70\n"
